        SalI restriction endonuclease site
        allows the introduction of coding sequences into this
        <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">vector</ENAMEX>. A <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">3</NUMEX>' splice site and polyadenylation signal has
        been incorporated to facilitate proper post-transciptional
