        nucleotides <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">29 to 626</NUMEX> of the 
        Neo coding sequence with an
        accompanying 
        pgk promoter flanked by 
        loxP elements. No G418 resistant
        <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">colonies</ENAMEX> were obtained when plasmids containing this
