        Neo cassette were introduced into
        wild type <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">ES</ENAMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="FAC_DESC">cells</ENAMEX> by electroporation (data not shown).
        This confirmed that deletion of the <ENAMEX TYPE="PRODUCT">3</ENAMEX>'-end of 
