        G418 [ <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">16</TIMEX>]. The <ENAMEX TYPE="PRODUCT">5</ENAMEX>' region of homology consisted of <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">4.5</NUMEX> kb
        of 
        Hnf3 α genomic sequence that extends
